R6L2, Palomides.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=callan@lighttanksofdaoc>Callan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#000000>(10/6/03 8:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=364.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Styles: Who *really* uses flank chain</span><hr size=1> Every chance I can. If I get the Hyp dark stun off, I strafe around for the flank/rain. If someone else has agro I use flank/rain. It hits very hard and from a huge arc around the target.<br>
