Just find the right position, very good if end regen is't avaible. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=blame@lighttanksofdaoc>Blame</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://homepages.internet.lu/lordoftherings/images/boromir.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Old-Timer</span><br>  Posts: 527<br> <font color=#000000>(10/7/03 7:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=364.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hmm</span><hr size=1> I haven't done RvR with Blame since 1.62, but I'm a sucker for positionals, and with Axe in Abermenai and Thidranki (and once so far in Caledon) I used the Pincer (side CS move) wherever possible. I think it would be fair to say that if my merc was in a position where he could pull off that move post 1.62, he would.<br>
<br>
In PvE (solo), here's now the perfect fight goes with me:<br>
<br>
Flank<br>
Rain<br>
Shadows (bleed)<br>
Reflection (this is truly the perfect time to parry!)<br>
Darkness<br>
Flank<br>
Rain<br>
Shadows (again)<br>
wait three swings inbetween each successive Shadows, to get some out of the ticking without blowing your End (i have had some _very_ slow fights with some mobs)<br>
If you parry again, use the Stun for a second and final time - good enough for you to pull off one more Rain combo if you're fast!<br>
<br>
So in the perfect 1v1 fight, I get Rain off 3 times... 4 sometimes if I'm very fast/lucky.<br>
<br>
Great move so long as the enemy is already bleeding and a nice speed debuff. If it's a tough (slash resistant for me) mob with lots of HP, DS does similar damage taking the bleed into account, but if you've got the effect, reap the DoT by using other more powerful, straightforward moves inbetween. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=danyan@lighttanksofdaoc>Danyan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Determined Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 213<br> <font color=#000000>(10/7/03 9:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=364.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: hmm</span><hr size=1> My perfect fight is:<br>
